#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.48"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.48:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.48:0.2"
msgid "5. Papātavagga "
msgstr "5. A Cliff "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 48. Dutiyachiggaḷayugasutta → dutiyachiggalasuttaṃ (bj) | chiggaḷa 3 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.48:0.3"
msgid "48. Dutiyachiggaḷayugasutta "
msgstr "48. A Yoke With a Hole (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.457, sc1
msgctxt "sn56.48:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ayaṃ mahāpathavī ekodakā assa. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose the earth was entirely covered with water. "

msgctxt "sn56.48:1.2"
msgid "Tatra puriso ekacchiggaḷaṃ yugaṃ pakkhipeyya. "
msgstr "And a person threw a yoke with a single hole into it. "

msgctxt "sn56.48:1.3"
msgid "Tamenaṃ puratthimo vāto pacchimena saṃhareyya, pacchimo vāto puratthimena saṃhareyya, uttaro vāto dakkhiṇena saṃhareyya, dakkhiṇo vāto uttarena saṃhareyya. "
msgstr "The east wind wafts it west; the west wind wafts it east; the north wind wafts it south; and the south wind wafts it north. "

msgctxt "sn56.48:1.4"
msgid "Tatrassa kāṇo kacchapo. So vassasatassa vassasatassa accayena sakiṃ sakiṃ ummujjeyya. "
msgstr "And there was a one-eyed turtle who popped up once every hundred years. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.48:1.5"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.48:1.6"
msgid "api nu kho kāṇo kacchapo vassasatassa vassasatassa accayena sakiṃ sakiṃ ummujjanto amusmiṃ ekacchiggaḷe yuge gīvaṃ paveseyyā”ti? "
msgstr "Would that one-eyed turtle, popping up once every hundred years, still poke its neck through the hole in that yoke?” "

# NOTE: Reading adhicca as “chance” (BB) or “coincidence” (Thanissaro) here are untenable.
#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.48:1.7"
msgid "“Adhiccamidaṃ, bhante, yaṃ so kāṇo kacchapo vassasatassa vassasatassa accayena sakiṃ sakiṃ ummujjanto amusmiṃ ekacchiggaḷe yuge gīvaṃ paveseyyā”ti. "
msgstr "“It’s unlikely, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn56.48:2.1"
msgid "“Evaṃ adhiccamidaṃ, bhikkhave, yaṃ manussattaṃ labhati. "
msgstr "“That’s how unlikely it is to get reborn as a human being. "

msgctxt "sn56.48:2.2"
msgid "Evaṃ adhiccamidaṃ, bhikkhave, yaṃ tathāgato loke uppajjati arahaṃ sammāsambuddho. "
msgstr "And that’s how unlikely it is for a Realized One to arise in the world, a perfected one, a fully awakened Buddha. "

msgctxt "sn56.48:2.3"
msgid "Evaṃ adhiccamidaṃ, bhikkhave, yaṃ tathāgatappavedito dhammavinayo loke dibbati. "
msgstr "And that’s how unlikely it is for the teaching and training proclaimed by a Realized One to shine in the world. "

#. VAR: Tassidaṃ → tayidaṃ (?)
msgctxt "sn56.48:2.4"
msgid "Tassidaṃ, bhikkhave, manussattaṃ laddhaṃ, tathāgato loke uppanno arahaṃ sammāsambuddho, tathāgatappavedito ca dhammavinayo loke dibbati. "
msgstr "And now, mendicants, you have been reborn as a human being. A Realized One has arisen in the world, a perfected one, a fully awakened Buddha. And the teaching and training proclaimed by a Realized One shines in the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn56.48:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.48:3.2"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

